  "description": "<i>Orto Puzzle</i> is an educational game for kids. The player's task is to choose the correct spelling. The correct spelling needs to be selected from two different letters. The game highlights a part of the word the player needs to decide on. If correct, the word is replaced by a part of the picture, if not, it remains on the board and deduct one life. All twelve words must be solved with up to three errors.<br><br>The game features built in spelling rules and allows to choose specified orthographic set of words. ",
